1. profile page:
user name - display
# of followers - take to another page, display all the number of followers with links to their profile page (show their posts in reverse order on click)
# of following - same as above for following users
my post - show all my posts in reverse order
networks - show all the users with follow or unfollow button
likes - show all the post like by current user

2. following button:
take to a page and show all the users that current user follows
on each user show their most latest posts alone in their bio. 
have a hyperlink to take to the user's profile page

number of pages: 

1. index : show all the posts from all the users
2. user_profile : show current user's profile, posts, networks,likes, and # of followers and following.
3. profile : (for users who are not logged in ) show all of their posts in reverse order
4. following: show the page only for logged in users, show limited posts.
